text: Kutuyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Urazovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 230 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Uchaly, 16 km from Urazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kutuyevo
